        <div class="row">
            <div class="col-xs-12 col-md-10 col-md-offset-1">
                <div class="blog-page__header">
                    <h1 class="h2">The Best Berry Beet Smoothie (with Shatavari)</h1>
                    <h5>04/25/2022</h5>
                                                                <h5>
                                                        <a href="/blog?category=13">Recipes</a>                                                </h5>
                                        <img width="862" height="575" src="https://organicindiausa.com/wp-content/uploads/beet-berry-smoothie-shatavari-862x575.jpg" class="blog-page__thumbnail wp-post-image" alt="Vibrant magenta beet vegan smoothie recipes in clear glass" decoding="async" loading="lazy" srcset="https://organicindiausa.com/wp-content/uploads/beet-berry-smoothie-shatavari-862x575.jpg 862w, https://organicindiausa.com/wp-content/uploads/beet-berry-smoothie-shatavari-300x200.jpg 300w, https://organicindiausa.com/wp-content/uploads/beet-berry-smoothie-shatavari-1024x683.jpg 1024w, https://organicindiausa.com/wp-content/uploads/beet-berry-smoothie-shatavari-768x512.jpg 768w, https://organicindiausa.com/wp-content/uploads/beet-berry-smoothie-shatavari-110x73.jpg 110w, https://organicindiausa.com/wp-content/uploads/beet-berry-smoothie-shatavari-419x279.jpg 419w, https://organicindiausa.com/wp-content/uploads/beet-berry-smoothie-shatavari-266x177.jpg 266w, https://organicindiausa.com/wp-content/uploads/beet-berry-smoothie-shatavari-334x223.jpg 334w, https://organicindiausa.com/wp-content/uploads/beet-berry-smoothie-shatavari.jpg 1200w" sizes="(max-width: 862px) 100vw, 862px" />                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
        
        <div class="row">
            <div class="col-xs-12 col-sm-10 col-sm-offset-1 col-md-8 col-md-offset-2">
                
                <div class="gutenberg-content">
                    
<p>Whose heart wouldn’t skip a ‘beet’ just taking in the gorgeous, vibrant color of this berry and beet smoothie? Simple to make, it’s a delectable way to celebrate Mother’s Day–and any day–that the whole family will enjoy. Best of all, this berrylicious beverage comes with some radiant health benefits, not least with the inclusion of our ORGANIC INDIA <a href="https://organicindiausa.com/shatavari/">Shatavari</a>.<br><br>An Ayurvedic herbal supplement for women that supports healthy hormone and reproductive functions, Shatavari can also help relieve stress, fight oxidative stress, maintain healthy blood sugar metabolism, and support a healthy inflammatory response. Although <a href="https://organicindiausa.com/shatavari/">Shatavari </a>is best known for supporting women’s wellness and vitality, it has also been used for men in combination with adaptogenic Ashwagandha for all-around hormonal support and balance. Feel free to combine both, or switch up supplements of choice, in this versatile recipe!<br><br>Beloved berries, a joy to snack on, are delicious, nutritious, and packed full of antioxidants. Key to the gemlike pop of color in this smoothie, beets are loaded with essential vitamins and minerals, including folate, which plays a key role in controlling damage to blood vessels, helping to reduce the risk of heart disease and stroke. While beetroot isn’t quite so lucky as berries when it comes to universal love, this luscious blend is sure to convert any skeptics and give Mother’s Day an extra special glow.</p>



<h2 class="wp-block-heading"><strong><br>Berry Beet Smoothie Recipe </strong></h2>



<figure class="wp-block-image size-large"><img decoding="async" loading="lazy" width="1024" height="683" src="https://organicindiausa.com/wp-content/uploads/beet-smoothie-shatavari-1024x683.jpg" alt="Vibrant magenta beet smoothie in clear glass with stainless steel straw." class="wp-image-3447" srcset="https://organicindiausa.com/wp-content/uploads/beet-smoothie-shatavari-1024x683.jpg 1024w, https://organicindiausa.com/wp-content/uploads/beet-smoothie-shatavari-300x200.jpg 300w, https://organicindiausa.com/wp-content/uploads/beet-smoothie-shatavari-768x512.jpg 768w, https://organicindiausa.com/wp-content/uploads/beet-smoothie-shatavari-110x73.jpg 110w, https://organicindiausa.com/wp-content/uploads/beet-smoothie-shatavari-419x279.jpg 419w, https://organicindiausa.com/wp-content/uploads/beet-smoothie-shatavari-266x177.jpg 266w, https://organicindiausa.com/wp-content/uploads/beet-smoothie-shatavari-334x223.jpg 334w, https://organicindiausa.com/wp-content/uploads/beet-smoothie-shatavari-862x575.jpg 862w, https://organicindiausa.com/wp-content/uploads/beet-smoothie-shatavari.jpg 1200w" sizes="(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px" /></figure>



<p><strong>Per 1 smoothie</strong></p>



<p><strong>Ingredients: </strong></p>



<ul><li>1 medium banana, cut into chunks and frozen</li><li>1 Cup frozen strawberries, or mixed berries</li><li>⅓ Cup grated raw beetroot (feel free to use cooked)</li><li>1 Cup plant milk of choice </li><li>½ Teaspoon (2 Capsules) <a href="https://shop.organicindiausa.com/products/shatavri?_pos=1&amp;_sid=05472cd88&amp;_ss=r">ORGANIC INDIA Shatavari</a></li><li>Optional: ¼ Cup yogurt of choice</li></ul>



<p><strong>Method: <br></strong>Place all ingredients into a blender or food processor. Blend until smooth. Enjoy!</p>



<p>Love smoothies? You have to try this <a href="https://organicindiausa.com/blog/mango-moringa-green-smoothie/">Mango Moringa Green Smoothie</a>! Perfect to switch off with this one for every day wellness. <br><br></p>
                </div>

